obj_root_law_sections_1_content:
  string
  line 1
  line `THE UNLAWFUL ACTIVITIES (PREVENTION) ACT, 1967`
  line ____________
  line `ARRANGEMENT OF SECTIONS`
  line ________
  line `CHAPTER I`
  line `P RELIMINARY`
  line `S ECTIONS`
  line `1. Short title, extent and application.`
  line `2. Definitions.`
  line `CHAPTER II`
  line `U NLAWFUL ASSOCIATION S`
  line `3. Declaration of an association as unlawful.`
  line `4. Reference to Tribunal.`
  line `5. Tribunal.`
  line `6. Period of operation and cancellation of notification.`
  line `7. Power to prohibit the use of funds of an unlawful association.`
  line `8. Power to notify places used for the purpose of an unlawful association.`
  line `9. Procedure to be followed in the disposal of applications under this Act.`
  line `CHAPTER III`
  line `O FFENCES AND PENALTIES`
  line `10. Penalty for being member of an unlawful association, etc.`
  line `11. Penalty for dealing with funds of an unlawful association.`
  line `12. Penalty for contravention of an order made in respect of a notified place.`
  line `13. Punishment for unlawful activities.`
  line `14. Offences to be cognizable.`
  line `CHAPTER IV`
  line `P UNISHMENT FOR TERRORIST ACTIVITIES`
  line `15. Terrorist act.`
  line `16. Punishment for t errorist a ct.`
  line `16A. [ Omitted ].`
  line `17. Punishment for raising fund s for terrorist act.`
  line `18. Punishment for c onspiracy, etc.`
  line `18A. Punishment for organi s ing of terrorist camps.`
  line `18B. Punishment for recruiting of any person or persons for terrorist act.`
  line `19. Punishment for h arbouring, etc.`
  line `20. Punishment for b eing m ember of t errorist g ang or o rganisation.`
  line `21. Punishment for h olding p roceeds of t errorism.`
  line `22. Punishment for threatening w itness.`
