  line `2. KHALISTAN COMMANDO FORCE.`
  line `3. KHALISTAN ZINDABAD FORCE.`
  line `4. INTERNATIONAL SIKH YOUTH FEDERATION.`
  line `5. LASHKAR - E - TAIBA/PASBAN - E - AHLE HADIS 3 [The Resistance Front and all its`
  line `manifestations and front Organisations].`
  line `6. JAISH - E - MOHAMMED/TAHRIK - E - FURQAN.`
  line `7. HARKAT - UL - MUJAHIDEEN/HARKAT - UL - ANSAR/HARKAT - U L - JEHAD - E - ISLAMI.`
  line `8. HIZB - UL - MUJAHIDEEN/HIZB - UL - MUJAHIDEEN PIR PANJAL REGIMENT.`
  line `9. AL - UMAR - MUJAHIDEEN.`
  line `10. JAMMU AND KASHMIR ISLAMIC FRONT.`
  line `11. UNITED LIBERATION FRONT OF ASSAM (ULFA).`
  line `12. NATIONAL DEMOCRATIC FRONT OF BODOLAND (NDFB).`
  line `13. PEOPLE ’ S LIBERATI ON ARMY (PLA).`
  line `14. UNITED NATIONAL LIBERATION FRONT (UNLF).`
  line `15. PEOPLE ’ S REVOLUTIONARY PARTY OF KANGLEIPAK (PREPAK).`
  line `16. KANGLEIPAK COMMUNIST PARTY (KCP).`
  line `17. KANGLEI YAOL KANBA LUP (KYKL).`
  line `18. MANIPUR PEOPLE ’ S LIBERATION FRONT (MPLF).`
  line `19. ALL TRIPURA TIGE R FORCE.`
  line `20. NATIONAL LIBERATION FRONT OF TRIPURA.`
  line `21. LIBERATION TIGERS OF TAMIL EELAM (LTTE).`
  line `22. STUDENTS ISLAMIC MOVEMENT OF INDIA.`
  line `23. DEENDAR ANJUMAN.`
  line `24. COMMUNIST PARTY OF INDIA (M ARXIST - LENINIST) — PEOPLE ’ S`
  line `WAR, ALLITS FORMATIONS AND FRONT ORGANISATIONS.`
  line `25. MAOIST COMMUNIST CENTRE (MCC), ALL ITS FORMATIONS AND FRONT`
  line ORGANISATIONS.
  line `26. AL BADR.`
  line `27. JAMIAT - UL - MUJAHIDDEN.`
  line `28. AL - QAIDA.`
  line `29. DUKHTARAN - E - MILLAT (DEM).`
  line `1. The Schedule renumbered as the First Schedule thereof by Act 3 of 2013, s. 14 (w.e.f. 1 - 2 - 2013).`
  line `2. Subs. by Act 28 of 2019, s. 10, for “ See sections 2( 1 ) ( m ) and 35” (w.e.f. 14 - 8 - 2019).`
  line `3. In s. by Notification No. S.O. 45(E), dated by 5th January, 2023.`
