  line 27
  line `30. TAMIL NADU LIBERATION ARMY (TNLA).`
  line `31. TAMIL NATIONAL RETRIEVAL TROOPS (TNR T).`
  line `32. AKHIL BHARAT NEPALI EKTA SAMAJ (ABNES).`
