  line `(Implementation of Security Council Resolutions) Order, 2007 made under section 2 of the`
  line `United Nations (Security Council) Act, 1947(43 of 1947) and amended from time to time.]`
  line `34. Akhil Bharat Nepali Ekta Samaj (ABNES)`
  line `2 [35. Indian Mijahideen, All Its formations and front organisations.]`
