  line `4 [37. Kamatapur Liberation Organisation, all its formations and front organizations.]`
  line `5 [38. Islamic State/Islamic State of Iraq and Levant/Islamic State of Iraq and Syria/Daish/ Islamic`
  line `State in Khorasan Province (ISKP)/ISIS Wilayat Khorasan/Islam ic State of Iraq and the Sham -`
  line `Khorasan (ISIS - K) and all its manifestations.]`
  line `6 [39. National Socialist Council of Nagaland (Khaplang) [NSCN(K)], all its formations and front`
  line organisations.]
  line `7 [40. The Khalistan Liberation Force and all its manifestations.]`
  line `8 [41. Tehreek - ul - Mujahideen (TuM) and all its manifestations.]`
  line `9 [42. Jamaat - ul - Mujahideen Bangladesh or Jamaat - ul - Mujahideen India or Jamaat - ul - Mujahideen`
  line `Hindustan and all its manifestations.]`
