obj_root_law_sections_29_content:
  string
  line 29
  line `1 [ THE THIRD SCHEDULE`
  line `[ S ee clause ( b ) of Explanation to s ection 15( 1 )]`
  line `SECURITY FEATURES TO DEFINE HIGH QUALITY COUNTERFEIT INDIAN CURRENCY`
  line NOTES
  line `Watermark(s), Security thread and any one of the following features:`
  line `(a) Latent image;`
  line `(b) See through registration;`
  line `(c) Print quality sharpness;`
  line `(d) Raised effect;`
  line `(e) Fluorescent characteristics;`
  line `(f) Substrate quality;`
  line `(g) Paper taggant;`
  line `(h) Colour shift effect in OVI;`
  line `(i) Colour shift effect in security thread.]`
  line `1. Subs. by G.S.R. 231(E), dated 18.03.2014.`
